scraper.utils

Class Elements

  • java.lang.Object
    • scraper.utils.Elements

  • public class Elements
extends java.lang.Object
    The Elements class represents a collection of HTML elements retrieved from a Document. It allows a user to iterate through each Element and process them in a manner similar to Java's Scanner class.
